{"tid":1140462,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"官宣了，夏薩特季尾離隊。","createTime":"2019-05-06T01:17:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T02:20:44.000Z","uid":16697,"like":13,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f71a412604f8ef640d845b0a1c356d7ad890037d","tid":1140462,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T01:17:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/2bad12/f/800x0/https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ItOJbR1EmQeuBcH95xb9aBPv8gU=/0x0:2098x3000/1200x800/filters:focal(1222x182:1556x516)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/63195021/887212224.jpg.0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2F2bad12%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fcdn.vox-cdn.com%2Fthumbor%2FItOJbR1EmQeuBcH95xb9aBPv8gU%3D%2F0x0%3A2098x3000%2F1200x800%2Ffilters%3Afocal%281222x182%3A1556x516%29%2Fcdn.vox-cdn.com%2Fuploads%2Fchorus_image%2Fimage%2F63195021%2F887212224.jpg.0.jpg&h=585272d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nChelsea Football Club has agreed terms with Cercle Bruges for the permanent transfer of Kylian Hazard.The 23-year-old Belgian, younger brother of Blues forward Eden, joined us from Hungarian side Ujpest in the summer of 2017, making 11 appearances for our development squad last season, including a goalscoring debut against Swansea City.Hazard has spent the current campaign on loan in his homeland&rsquo;s top flight with Cercle Bruges, scoring four goals in 21 appearances in all competitions, and will make the move permanent when the summer transfer window opens.<br />\nWe thank Kylian for his service to the club and wish him the best of luck for the next chapter of his career.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chelseafc.com/en/news/2019/05/04/kylian-hazard-to-leave-chelsea?fbclid=IwAR3G053zs9oBkTwXWJpcx34eBiZ8hMp8Wrilnk7soCBoSmFVTcQtKH9ycbk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chelseafc.com%2Fen%2Fnews%2F2019%2F05%2F04%2Fkylian-hazard-to-leave-chelsea%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3G053zs9o